<br>
Anyway. I'm looking to move on. I'd like to start experiencing the high end of the game. Comet Nosce couldn't even agree to organize for North Temple of Veeshan...<br>
<br>
I read that AD is looking for some new monks, so I thought I'd give it a try.<br>
<br>
My Magelo profile in my signiture can help explain my situation a bit better.<br>
<br>
Right now I have 54 AA points.. however I still have quite a ways to go before I meet your guild's requirements. I still need Rapid Feign 3, Natural Durability 3, and the sensei title overall. As it stands I'll need at least 30 more AA's.<br>
<br>
(This post is basicly just a very VERY early application.)<br>
<br>
I have good street cred, a good guild record, and my guildmembers would often refer to me to learn about something in the game. I have a great knowledge of the game and they would always come to me for advice.. sometimes so much that it annoyed me.<br>
<br>
Anyway.. If there's anything further I need to know, please answer, or contact me in the game. I'll update when I get closer to getting Sensei title. <p>-Yuffie<br>
